<!doctype html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>お問い合わせ | 時短 × 健康</title>
    <meta name="description" content="記事の誤り・改善提案・サービスに関するお問い合わせはこちらからどうぞ。" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://jitan-kenko.blog/contact/" />
  </head>
  <body>

    <header class="site-header">
      <div class="container">
        <a href="/" class="brand">
          <span class="brand-name">時短 × 健康</span>
          <span class="brand-sub">自分の状態にあった自己管理を</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <div class="container page-wrap">

        <h1 class="page-title">お問い合わせ</h1>

        <section class="section">
          <div class="notice">
            <p>記事内容の誤り・改善提案・サービスに関するご質問などお気軽にどうぞ。</p>
            <p class="caution">※ 個別の症状・診断・治療に関するご相談はお受けできません。医療に関するご相談はかかりつけ医にご相談ください。</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <div class="form-wrap">
            <iframe
              src="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSflX6bfUhbKTOiB-N_3w6ll9RntGxUbj1gz-slkkMOE-GpOOA/viewform?embedded=true"
              width="100%"
              height="780"
              frameborder="0"
              marginheight="0"
              marginwidth="0"
            >読み込んでいます…</iframe>
          </div>
        </section>

      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer">
      <div class="container footer-inner">
        <p>&copy; 2026 長友恭平</p>
        <nav class="footer-nav">
          <a href="/privacy">プライバシーポリシー</a>
          <a href="/disclaimer">免責事項</a>
          <a href="/about">このブログについて</a>
          <a href="/contact">お問い合わせ</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>

<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { font-size: 16px; }
body {
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN',
               'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  background: #f7f5f1;
  color: #212b38;
  line-height: 1.8;
}
a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
.container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }

.site-header {
  background: #0f2545;
  padding: 1rem 0;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
}
.brand { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.1rem; }
.brand-name { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; line-height: 1.2; }
.brand-sub  { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #93c5fd; font-weight: 400; }

.page-wrap { padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem; }
.page-title {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #1b3f6e;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #c4703b;
}
.section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }

.notice {
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid #e0dbd2;
  border-left: 4px solid #c4703b;
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
}
.notice p {
  font-size: 0.92rem;
  color: #536070;
  line-height: 1.9;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.notice p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.caution {
  font-size: 0.83rem !important;
  color: #8fa0b0 !important;
}

.form-wrap {
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid #e0dbd2;
  border-radius: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.form-wrap iframe {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  border: none;
}

.site-footer {
  background: #0f2545;
  color: #94a3b8;
  padding: 1.5rem 0;
  font-size: 0.78rem;
}
.footer-inner { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
.footer-nav   { display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.footer-nav a { color: #94a3b8; }
.footer-nav a:hover { color: #e2e8f0; }
</style>
